# Hugo knowledgebase — build artifacts
/public/
/resources/_gen/
.hugo_build.lock

# content/ is generated from assets/content/ + docs/ by
# utils/build-kb-content.mjs; never committed.
/content/

# NOTE: data/api-symbols.json is intentionally NOT ignored. It is generated by
# the TypeDoc symbol-map plugin (npm run docs) but committed — like
# type-catalog.md — so the KB deploy (which does not run TypeDoc) can consume it
# for {@link} resolution in the dev docs. Regenerate it with `npm run docs`.
